Question: IN at least one image there is only a single violin and  saxophone set against darkness.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: http://www.mermaidmuse.com/images/together.jpg

Right image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/e4/c9/cc/e4c9cc0d531ab8f2aef518ae464507d0.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many violins are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many violins are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many saxophones are in the image?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many saxophones are in the image?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the image set against darkness?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the image set against darkness?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER2} == 1 and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 1 and {ANSWER3} == 1 and {ANSWER5}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} or {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
```
